        <dc:creator><![CDATA[sylumer]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>If Craft supports adding such a URL (not all apps recognise all URL schemes), then you simply create the URL as per the Drafts URL scheme documentation. Substitute in the name of your workspace (URL encode the name (you can Google an encoder if you need one), if your workspace name contains any non-alphanumeric characters just to be sure it is added to the URL correctly).</p>
